          "$(x + 7)^2$",
          "$x(x - 49)$"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Difference of squares: $x^2 - 49 = (x + 7)(x - 7)$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Factor completely: $2x^2 + 7x - 15$",
        "options": [
