        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Factors of $2 \\times (-15) = -30$ that sum to 7: 10 and -3. $2x^2 + 10x - 3x - 15 = 2x(x + 5) - 3(x + 5) = (2x - 3)(x + 5)$."
      },
